{
    "name": "Dream Spider",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Dream Spider",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Venom Addicts",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Talented alchemists process dream spider venom into an addictive drug. Those who become addicted can be driven in desperation to seek out dream spiders and allow the creatures to bite their flesh to get their fix\u2014an arrangement that backfires horribly as the spiders feed.",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Monster Core 2",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 302",
                                "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 302",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 276
                            },
                            "page": 302
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Additional Lore",
                        "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                    }
                }
            ],
            "text": "A dream spider's webs have an iridescent hue and are infused with the same hallucinogenic compound as the creature's toxin. Originally denizens of tropical jungles, dream spiders have adapted well to temperate environments, particularly thriving among the rooftops of cities where shady alchemists use their venom to produce addictive drugs.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Monster Core 2",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 302",
                        "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 302",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 276
                    },
                    "page": 302
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
